&nbsp; 
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;

Lead the technical vision for our campaign optimization roadmap, translating high-level objectives into data science products.

Architect and deploy end-to-end uplift models and optimization systems that maximize our investment efficiency.

Design and execute advanced experimentation frameworks to reliably measure campaign incrementality.

Set the gold standard for technical excellence by championing rigorous statistical and engineering practices.

